---
import Layout from '../../components/Layout.astro';
import { getContent } from '../../utils/content';

const content = await getContent('en');
---

<Layout title="About Mikhail - Pravilo.Club" description="Learn about Mikhail Bondaruk, master of Pravilo and wellness practitioner" lang="en">
  <main class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="page-title">About Mikhail</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">Master of Pravilo, wellness practitioner, and adventurer</p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <section class="section story-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">My Journey</h2>
      <div class="story-content">
        <div class="story-text">
          <p>My path began with a deep interest in the body and health. I studied at a sports college, then at a physical education university in Moscow. But the most important lessons I received were not from books, but from living experience—through travel, exploration, and personal experiments with body and consciousness.</p>
          
          <p>From a young age, I was drawn to freedom and exploring the limits of human potential. I spent many years hitchhiking across Russia and post-Soviet countries, traveling almost the entire southern coast of the country. Then I went further—to Asia. I visited Thailand, Malaysia, Indonesia, Cambodia, Vietnam. I lived for a long time in India and South Korea. These travels taught me lightness, the ability to adapt, and to see beauty in simplicity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="story-image">
          <div class="image-placeholder">
            <p>Mikhail's Journey</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section practices-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">My Practices</h2>
      <div class="practices-grid">
        <div class="practice-card">
          <h3>Massage Therapy</h3>
          <p>I work as a massage master—relieving spasms, working on trigger points, restoring body mobility. I have an individual approach: sometimes gentle, sometimes deep, but always with attention to the person.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="practice-card">
          <h3>Alpha Gravity System</h3>
          <p>I teach the Alpha Gravity system and create Pravilo simulators that help develop strength, flexibility, and ligament health.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="practice-card">
          <h3>Cold Therapy</h3>
          <p>I practice hardening—I walk in shorts and t-shirt all year round, even in winter. This practice strengthens the immune system and builds mental resilience.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="practice-card">
          <h3>Breathing & Spiritual Practices</h3>
          <p>I use breathing techniques, prayers, and internal gratitude practices. I believe that health begins not only with the body but also with the soul, with inner connection to God and the universe.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section nutrition-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Nutrition Experiments</h2>
      <div class="nutrition-content">
        <div class="nutrition-text">
          <p>Nutrition became a real laboratory for me. I tried different systems: vegetarianism, veganism, raw foodism. In the end, I was on raw food for eight years, of which three and a half years were pure fruitarianism. Later I added softer regimes. These years showed me how nutrition affects the body and psyche, energy levels, and clarity of consciousness.</p>
          
          <p>I practiced long-term fasting, did cleanses, including with castor oil, drank fresh juices. All this was part of a big experiment in self-recovery. I realized that the body can renew itself and launch its regenerative processes if given the right conditions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="nutrition-benefits">
          <h3>What I Learned</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>How nutrition affects energy and consciousness</li>
            <li>The body's ability to regenerate and heal</li>
            <li>Different approaches to cleansing and detoxification</li>
            <li>The connection between food and spiritual practice</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section talents-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Beyond Body Work</h2>
      <div class="talents-grid">
        <div class="talent-card">
          <h3>Music</h3>
          <p>I'm a musician, I play the jaw harp and harmonica. Music for me is a way to connect with myself and people. I create unique sounds that resonate with the soul.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="talent-card">
          <h3>Handicrafts</h3>
          <p>I create jewelry from wire and crystals. For me, this is a meditative process in which unique things are born. Each piece carries energy and intention.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="talent-card">
          <h3>Travel</h3>
          <p>Travel continues to be part of me. I believe that the world is our greatest teacher, and every journey brings new insights and growth.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section philosophy-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">My Philosophy</h2>
      <div class="philosophy-content">
        <div class="philosophy-text">
          <p>I've experienced many challenges and losses. There were difficult periods—loss of home, business, family. At some point, I found myself in survival mode. But it was this that made me deeper. I learned to perceive events as facts, not just as emotions. I understood that emotions are energy: they can nourish us or destroy us. It all depends on quality and direction.</p>
          
          <p>My philosophy of relationships, for example, is built on trust and sincerity. I see them as a common "well of energy" from which two people can draw if they take care of it together.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="philosophy-principles">
          <h3>Core Principles</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Trust and Sincerity:</strong> The foundation of all relationships</li>
            <li><strong>Energy Awareness:</strong> Understanding emotions as energy</li>
            <li><strong>Continuous Growth:</strong> Never stopping the search for improvement</li>
            <li><strong>Nature Connection:</strong> Learning from the natural world</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Ready to Begin Your Journey?</h2>
        <p>Let me guide you on your path to health, freedom, and harmony. Together, we'll explore the ancient power of Pravilo and discover your potential.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/en/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Session</a>
          <a href="/en/services" class="btn btn-secondary">View Services</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #1a1a1a 100%);
    color: #ffffff;
    padding: 6rem 0 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #d4af37;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #d4af37;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .story-section {
    background: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .story-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .story-text p {
    color: #cccccc;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .story-image {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .image-placeholder {
    background: #333;
    border: 2px solid #d4af37;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: #d4af37;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .practices-section {
    background: #000;
  }

  .practices-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .practice-card {
    background: #1a1a1a;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 15px;
    border: 1px solid #333;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .practice-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: #d4af37;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);
  }

  .practice-card h3 {
    color: #d4af37;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .practice-card p {
    color: #cccccc;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .nutrition-section {
    background: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .nutrition-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .nutrition-text p {
    color: #cccccc;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .nutrition-benefits {
    background: #000;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border-left: 4px solid #d4af37;
  }

  .nutrition-benefits h3 {
    color: #d4af37;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .nutrition-benefits ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .nutrition-benefits li {
    color: #cccccc;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .nutrition-benefits li:before {
    content: "•";
    color: #d4af37;
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
  }

  .talents-section {
    background: #000;
  }

  .talents-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .talent-card {
    background: #1a1a1a;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 15px;
    border: 1px solid #333;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .talent-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: #d4af37;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);
  }

  .talent-card h3 {
    color: #d4af37;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .talent-card p {
    color: #cccccc;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .philosophy-section {
    background: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .philosophy-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .philosophy-text p {
    color: #cccccc;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .philosophy-principles {
    background: #000;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border-left: 4px solid #d4af37;
  }

  .philosophy-principles h3 {
    color: #d4af37;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .philosophy-principles ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .philosophy-principles li {
    color: #cccccc;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .philosophy-principles strong {
    color: #d4af37;
  }

  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #000000 100%);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #d4af37;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: #cccccc;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: #d4af37;
    color: #000;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #ff6b35;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: #d4af37;
    border: 2px solid #d4af37;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: #d4af37;
    color: #000;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
    
    .story-content,
    .nutrition-content,
    .philosophy-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .practices-grid,
    .talents-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>
